column4: Chipmaker Nvidia accelerates move into smarter automobiles
column5: Chipmaker Nvidia on Sunday unveiled a new processor aimed at powering high-end graphics on car dashboards as well as sophisticated auto-pilot systems.

column4: Qualcomm flicks switch on Internet-connected light bulbs
column5: SAN FRANCISCO Qualcomm on Monday unveiled easy-to-use blueprints to help manufacturers make LED light bulbs that use the chipmaker's wifi technology to connect to the Internet.
